{"tid":2200600,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"慢必: 快必已排期於本周四在高院進行上訴保釋 明日有另案於東區法院應訊","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T12:54:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c84b9ac273272699c9d41d9fd2c2d092b9b38267","tid":2200600,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志上周遭警方控以「發表煽動文字罪」等6罪後，上周二保釋申請被拒，至今已被扣押於荔枝角收押所5天。政府以言入罪，快必戰友、人民力量議員「慢必」陳志全今天會代他到觀塘及藍田如常開設「抗疫」街站，「人人都是譚得志」，向街坊派口罩及講述快必最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n慢必在其YouTube頻道透露，「劉公子」劉定成及張大衛牧師昨天探過快必，快必亦已排期於本周四在高院進行上訴保釋，若成功便可重見天日，繼續開街站與市民見面，而快必亦要於周一下午2時，就今年5月24日於銅鑼灣開街站而遭警方拘捕的案件於東區裁判法院應訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/7DJZO7HJWVDEHD4ZQXV2RRWMNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2F7DJZO7HJWVDEHD4ZQXV2RRWMNE%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513T%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=d09b003a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2F7DJZO7HJWVDEHD4ZQXV2RRWMNE%2F&h=557c780f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/7DJZO7HJWVDEHD4ZQXV2RRWMNE/</a>"},{"pid":"20c92eaa5410c5fcaefe18c8994235f6fe89885a","tid":2200600,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"撐快必慢必"},{"pid":"716596d1d961381e11b207ddbad3bc3ef922652a","tid":2200600,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c92eaa5410c5fcaefe18c8994235f6fe89885a","tid":2200600,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"撐快必慢必"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n